Class JunctionSpace

java.lang.Object
Space
MagentaSpace
JunctionSpace
public class JunctionSpace
extends MagentaSpace
This class defines the JunctionSpace, which is a MagentaSpace that prompts the user to decide where to go. This class inherits from the MagentaSpace class.
